  "source_text": {
    "text_id": "text_001",
    "title": "下班后的闲聊与内心独白",
    "source": "教师提供",
    "raw_text": "我看了眼时钟，拒绝了加班，露出微笑，伸手关掉了电脑。\n\n我们两人一起下楼，走向星巴克。我看着红衣服的同事，他挥了挥手，我们便坐了下来。\n\n同事和我聊起天来：“这天气时晴时阴，眼看又要下雨了……”\n我听着，心里有点无奈，又有点不安。\n我笑着说：“来杯咖啡和牛角包。”\n同事笑着回应：“我来杯绿茶，再加个苹果。”\n\n我们坐着，有一搭没一搭地聊着天。\n同事端着绿茶说：“看世界杯，巴西对葡萄牙！”我忍不住笑了。\n我捧着咖啡说：“看这球赛的精彩瞬间！”\n同事又说：“最近在找房子。”\n我接话：“刚看新闻，说房价跌了。”\n我又补了句：“不过油价倒是涨了！”\n同事说：“我看股票涨了。”\n同事又吐槽：“油价涨得离谱，车都快开不起了！”他看起来有点生气。\n我叹了口气：“我看的股票跌了。”\n同事说：“汇率倒是涨了。”\n\n我们就这么聊着天。\n我们挥手告别，他下楼，我往楼上走。\n时钟滴答走着，我上了楼，左转右转，朝着洗手间走去。\n我心里想着卫生棉条的事，走进洗手间，看着棉条，拉上了隔间的拉链。\n我看着棉条，发了会儿呆。\n走出隔间，我有点懵，耳边好像响起了音乐，看着不远处的女生，她回头看了我一眼。\n我看着她，想起她整理衣服的样子，心里有点心动。\n时钟继续走着，我往工位走，想起了垃圾分类的事。\n我把垃圾丢了，走回工位，坐了下来。",
    "notes": "包含对话、动作和心理活动的自然段落。"
  },
  "units": [
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_001",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看了眼时钟，拒绝了加班，露出微笑，伸手关掉了电脑。",
      "sentence_index": 1,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 36,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_002",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们两人一起下楼，走向星巴克。",
      "sentence_index": 2,
      "char_start": 38,
      "char_end": 55,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_003",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着红衣服的同事，他挥了挥手，我们便坐了下来。",
      "sentence_index": 3,
      "char_start": 55,
      "char_end": 82,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_004",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事和我聊起天来：“这天气时晴时阴，眼看又要下雨了……”",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "char_start": 84,
      "char_end": 116,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_005",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我听着，心里有点无奈，又有点不安。",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "char_start": 117,
      "char_end": 138,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_006",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我笑着说：“来杯咖啡和牛角包。”",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "char_start": 141,
      "char_end": 158,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_007",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事笑着回应：“我来杯绿茶，再加个苹果。”",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "char_start": 161,
      "char_end": 184,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_008",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们坐着，有一搭没一搭地聊着天。",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "char_start": 186,
      "char_end": 209,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_009",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事端着绿茶说：“看世界杯，巴西对葡萄牙！”我忍不住笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "char_start": 210,
      "char_end": 242,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_010",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我捧着咖啡说：“看这球赛的精彩瞬间！”",
      "sentence_index": 10,
      "char_start": 242,
      "char_end": 265,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_011",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事又说：“最近在找房子。”",
      "sentence_index": 11,
      "char_start": 268,
      "char_end": 284,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_012",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我接话：“刚看新闻，说房价跌了。”",
      "sentence_index": 12,
      "char_start": 285,
      "char_end": 304,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_013",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我又补了句：“不过油价倒是涨了！”",
      "sentence_index": 13,
      "char_start": 304,
      "char_end": 323,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_014",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事说：“我看股票涨了。”",
      "sentence_index": 14,
      "char_start": 325,
      "char_end": 340,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_015",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事又吐槽：“油价涨得离谱，车都快开不起了！”他看起来有点生气。",
      "sentence_index": 15,
      "char_start": 342,
      "char_end": 381,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_016",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我叹了口气：“我看的股票跌了。”",
      "sentence_index": 16,
      "char_start": 383,
      "char_end": 401,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_017",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事说：“汇率倒是涨了。”",
      "sentence_index": 17,
      "char_start": 403,
      "char_end": 418,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_018",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们就这么聊着天。",
      "sentence_index": 18,
      "char_start": 420,
      "char_end": 432,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_019",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们挥手告别，他下楼，我往楼上走。",
      "sentence_index": 19,
      "char_start": 434,
      "char_end": 456,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_020",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "时钟滴答走着，我上了楼，左转右转，朝着洗手间走去。",
      "sentence_index": 20,
      "char_start": 458,
      "char_end": 490,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_021",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我心里想着卫生棉条的事，走进洗手间，看着棉条，拉上了隔间的拉链。",
      "sentence_index": 21,
      "char_start": 492,
      "char_end": 532,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_022",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着棉条，发了会儿呆。",
      "sentence_index": 22,
      "char_start": 534,
      "char_end": 548,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_023",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走出隔间，我有点懵，耳边好像响起了音乐，看着不远处的女生，她回头看了我一眼。",
      "sentence_index": 23,
      "char_start": 550,
      "char_end": 598,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_024",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着她，想起她整理衣服的样子，心里有点心动。",
      "sentence_index": 24,
      "char_start": 600,
      "char_end": 628,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_025",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "时钟继续走着，我往工位走，想起了垃圾分类的事。",
      "sentence_index": 25,
      "char_start": 630,
      "char_end": 658,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_026",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我把垃圾丢了，走回工位，坐了下来。",
      "sentence_index": 26,
      "char_start": 660,
      "char_end": 680,
      "children": []
    }
  ],
